    • Method Detail

      • uiReadyTripRU

        public static TripRUBuilder uiReadyTripRU()
        Creates a UI ready TripRU, with the following fields set:
        • Policy - set to a new UI ready travel policy, unless policy is set via an explicit call to onPolicy, or this builder is called via policyBuilder.withRiskUnit, in which case th specified policy is used instead
        • RUNumber - set to the next available integer for TripRUs
        • TripDescription - set to a string of the form "Trip N"
            If used standalone this builder will not create a claim. To create it as part of a claim use 
               ClaimBuilder.uiReadyTravel()
       .withPolicy(PolicyBuilder.uiReadyTravel()
           .withRiskUnit(TripRUBuilder.uiReadyTripRU()))
        Returns:
